    {
      "text": "Indexed\nfolder 01 - 024}\n520\n\nPremise: Things are inside out (but will at the \"apocalypse\" assume their real shape). Therefore the right place to look for the Almighty is e.g. in the trash in the alley. + for Satan: in vast cathedrals, etc. Through enantiodromia they will \"on that day\" assume their rightful shapes - the great reversal. The Jester in the Tarot deck is the real King; the King card is the deranged one, the witless one. \"Ubik\" in its commercials + final theophany shows this reversal",
      "matched_alias": "Burroughs",
      "term_id": "TERM_burroughs",
      "term_name": "Burroughs",
      "term_slug": "burroughs"
    },
    {
      "text": "514\n\nLet me run a fantasy number by my scanner. The real world came to an end circa 45-70 C.E., an instant before the Parousia (i.e. the space-time of Acts): world qua real world was halted - frozen just before annihilation (this annihilation was the end of the 2nd epoch of the Torah -justice + severe limitation- + its end was to make way for the 3rd epoch, that of mercy (Christ's rule/return). But the 3rd epoch [of the Torah] never arrived; for us, anyhow. A counterfeit world (or creation) such",
      "matched_alias": "Form World",
      "term_id": "TERM_form-world",
      "term_name": "Form World",
      "term_slug": "form-world"
    }
